{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/COMMAND_GIANTS.png?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to command immense units, each with its own unique attack style and role in battle. Apoceus elevates the combat experience with these massive units, adding a new layer of strategic depth. With such colossal forces in play, you'll find every battle to be a thrilling and dynamic experience, where the might and tactics of your units can make all the difference in achieving victory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/Apoceus_GIF_Video_05_Resize.gif?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/DISCOVER_APOCEUS.png?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The World of Apoceus echoes out with a song of war,  with the promise of glory your armies follow your command to claim what is rightfully yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Apoceus unmatched in scale invites you to a real time strategy game that combines the traditional real time strategy elements and extends it ever further in a massive scale. All set in a new incredible fantasy universe for you as a player to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/Apoceus_GIF_Video_01_Resize.gif?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/UNBREAKABLE.png?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take command of the Dwarves, masters of technology, mining, and firepower. Proud and dedicated warriors have united to liberate themselves from the tyrannical reign of the Dwarven King, Restoring freedom to the Dwarven society and resurrecting the Clan system to its former glory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/Apoceus_GIF_Video_02_Resize.gif?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/LEADERSHIP.png?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In &quot;Apoceus,&quot; the trio of generals Hogwald, Allarah, and Xeth each with their distinct abilities, dramatically shape the gameplay. General Xeth, mysterious and powerful, is central to the gameplay. General Hogwald, representing the Dwarven faction, is a seasoned warrior and tactician. General Allarah, exclusively commanding the Dwarf Ranger unit, is renowned for expertise in tracking, stealth, and ranged combat, adding a layer of specialized strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/Apoceus_GIF_Video_03_Resize.gif?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/EXPANSION.png?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Apoceus offers a realm of exploration and strategic depth. The grand scale of the maps encourages a sense of adventure and discovery, inviting players to not just engage in battles but also to expand and explore. You'll experience huge maps and large-scale battles, where you can command up to 10,000 units. This blend of expansive landscapes and vast armies offers a deeply immersive RTS experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/Apoceus_GIF_Video_04_Resize.gif?t=1737552304\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737552304","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/page.bg.jpg?t=1737552304","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737552304","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737552304","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"HDR available","id":61}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/COMMAND_GIANTS.png?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to command immense units, each with its own unique attack style and role in battle. Apoceus elevates the combat experience with these massive units, adding a new layer of strategic depth. With such colossal forces in play, you'll find every battle to be a thrilling and dynamic experience, where the might and tactics of your units can make all the difference in achieving victory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/Apoceus_GIF_Video_05_Resize.gif?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\