. General Allarah, exclusively commanding the Dwarf Ranger unit, is renowned for expertise in tracking, stealth, and ranged combat, adding a layer of specialized strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/Apoceus_GIF_Video_03_Resize.gif?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/EXPANSION.png?t=1737552304\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Apoceus offers a realm of exploration and strategic depth. The grand scale of the maps encourages a sense of adventure and discovery, inviting players to not just engage in battles but also to expand and explore. You'll experience huge maps and large-scale battles, where you can command up to 10,000 units. This blend of expansive landscapes and vast armies offers a deeply immersive RTS experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/extras/Apoceus_GIF_Video_04_Resize.gif?t=1737552304\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Landell Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1841690/header.jpg?t=1737552304","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> TBA</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> TBA</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> TBA</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> TBA</li></ul>"}